1
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:35,040
=Love Again=

2
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:38,140
=Episode 32=

3
00:01:39,711 --> 00:01:40,555
Here you go.

4
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:41,290
Okay.

5
00:01:41,822 --> 00:01:42,610
I'm heading back.

6
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,290
Please come in.

7
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:04,640
Sure.

8
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,680
We're back.

9
00:02:08,730 --> 00:02:09,480
Dad, you're home.

10
00:02:10,288 --> 00:02:11,311
- It's all done.
- Lina.

11
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,200
I'm so sorry.

12
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,480
I'll put these things away.

13
00:02:17,333 --> 00:02:18,570
The bed sheets and blanket cover

14
00:02:18,610 --> 00:02:20,080
in Shen Dai's room are all new.

15
00:02:20,480 --> 00:02:21,760
The blanket has been aired out.

16
00:02:21,822 --> 00:02:23,190
Sorry to bother you for a few days.

17
00:02:24,610 --> 00:02:25,290
Don't be.

18
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,422
Go ahead and settle in.

19
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:38,480
This is Dai's room.

20
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:40,570
Stay here,

21
00:02:41,066 --> 00:02:42,200
and you'll be all right.

22
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,610
It's a good place.

23
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,290
Well,

24
00:02:44,888 --> 00:02:45,680
take some rest.

25
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,440
Sure.

26
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,000
Thank you.

27
00:02:49,266 --> 00:02:50,210
If you need anything,

28
00:02:50,555 --> 00:02:51,422
just let me know.

29
00:03:09,210 --> 00:03:09,850
Ms. Le,

30
00:03:09,888 --> 00:03:10,920
just relax and stay here.

31
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,111
Treat it like your home.

32
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,050
Thank you, Dai.

33
00:04:49,850 --> 00:04:50,880
Why are you still up?

34
00:04:51,622 --> 00:04:52,770
Having trouble sleeping?

35
00:04:59,170 --> 00:04:59,880
I can't sleep.

36
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:03,850
I saw Shen Qing

37
00:05:03,850 --> 00:05:06,090
take down the photo.

38
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,730
It must be hard for him.

39
00:05:10,222 --> 00:05:11,480
He didn't have to do that.

40
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,480
Shen Qing is always considerate.

41
00:05:15,090 --> 00:05:16,530
He takes care of everyone's feelings.

42
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:34,090
I thought the hard times were over,

43
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,920
but they weren't.

44
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,880
It's all in my head.

45
00:05:43,355 --> 00:05:44,933
Now, it's all coming flooding back.

46
00:05:52,210 --> 00:05:53,770
I've always felt like

47
00:05:54,050 --> 00:05:54,880
duckweed.

48
00:05:55,970 --> 00:05:56,970
It looks all green

49
00:05:58,210 --> 00:05:59,440
on the surface,

50
00:05:59,440 --> 00:05:59,880
but

51
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,360
underneath,

52
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,610
it has no roots.

53
00:06:08,730 --> 00:06:09,440
I didn't know

54
00:06:12,090 --> 00:06:13,410
someone who laughs a lot like you

55
00:06:15,970 --> 00:06:18,050
could carry so much sorrow.

56
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:23,410
This is unfair, Mr. Shen.

57
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:29,050
I'm the victim.

58
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:33,090
Why, after all these years,

59
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,320
am I still being bullied?

60
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,730
That's because you never fought back.

61
00:06:41,050 --> 00:06:42,410
You're all alone.

62
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,440
But you have me.

63
00:06:45,650 --> 00:06:46,970
We will fight back together.

64
00:06:49,290 --> 00:06:50,440
We must make sure the bad guy

65
00:06:51,050 --> 00:06:52,290
pays for what he did.

66
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,560
What are you up to, Liu?

67
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,800
Try to rebel?

68
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,290
No, I'm chopping the fish.

69
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:40,890
I see.

70
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,960
Once you're done,

71
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,770
I'll bring it over to Lina.

72
00:07:45,050 --> 00:07:45,370
Sure.

73
00:07:46,890 --> 00:07:47,770
The fish is huge.

74
00:07:49,170 --> 00:07:49,920
Do it gently.

75
00:07:50,050 --> 00:07:51,290
Move aside. I got this.

76
00:07:52,370 --> 00:07:53,370
Chop it smaller.

77
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,290
I know.

78
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,250
Good morning, Mr. Shen.

79
00:08:00,250 --> 00:08:01,320
Good morning.

80
00:08:02,490 --> 00:08:02,800
Come.

81
00:08:03,155 --> 00:08:04,133
Have some breakfast.

82
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,080
That's a feast.

83
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,010
Thank you.

84
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:09,530
Plain congee and some sides.

85
00:08:10,080 --> 00:08:11,890
A simple meal is a delight.

86
00:08:15,155 --> 00:08:15,840
How was it?

87
00:08:16,490 --> 00:08:17,720
Did you sleep well last night?

88
00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:21,960
I slept well
in the second half of the night.

89
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:23,890
I had a dream.

90
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:28,170
I dreamt of my dad and mom.

91
00:08:28,410 --> 00:08:31,250
We were sleeping together
in the same bed.

92
00:08:31,488 --> 00:08:32,560
You must be very happy.

93
00:08:33,050 --> 00:08:34,650
It was a long dream.

94
00:08:34,650 --> 00:08:35,800
My mom told me,

95
00:08:37,355 --> 00:08:39,130
"You don't have to be afraid anymore.

96
00:08:39,130 --> 00:08:40,920
We're all together now."

97
00:08:41,530 --> 00:08:42,010
Right?

98
00:08:42,680 --> 00:08:44,200
She's telling you not to be afraid.

99
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,320
This is home.

100
00:08:45,755 --> 00:08:47,022
Just stay here without worries.

101
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,050
Oh,

102
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:49,650
Dai called and said

103
00:08:49,666 --> 00:08:51,590
she'd be staying in Shanghai
for a few more days.

104
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:52,440
Isn't that perfect?

105
00:08:54,490 --> 00:08:56,650
That's good. If so, I'll stay

106
00:08:57,050 --> 00:08:57,720
a few more days.

107
00:08:58,488 --> 00:08:59,888
I'll treat this as home.

108
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:00,800
Welcome.

109
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,490
Sorry.

110
00:09:03,619 --> 00:09:04,970
(Heibao)

111
00:09:05,890 --> 00:09:06,410
It's Heibao.

112
00:09:08,050 --> 00:09:09,650
Maybe it's about my dog.

113
00:09:10,250 --> 00:09:10,960
You take it.

114
00:09:14,290 --> 00:09:14,770
Heibao.

115
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,720
Shuishan,

116
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:17,890
Oppo won't eat at home,

117
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,770
so I brought him here.

118
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:21,440
Where are you?

119
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:23,130
I'm downstairs at Shen's place.

120
00:09:23,490 --> 00:09:23,920
Come down.

121
00:09:28,410 --> 00:09:29,600
Oppo won't eat,

122
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,410
so he brought him over.

123
00:09:31,977 --> 00:09:32,890
They're downstairs.

124
00:09:32,933 --> 00:09:33,650
You should go.

125
00:09:36,130 --> 00:09:36,840
Come with me.

126
00:09:37,370 --> 00:09:38,650
No, you go ahead.

127
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,010
All right. I'll be back shortly.

128
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:42,370
I'll head down to check.

129
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:30,800
Hello?

130
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,320
Sun,

131
00:10:34,170 --> 00:10:35,370
are you doing your job right?

132
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:36,920
There's a big black guy

133
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,130
bringing a dog inside.

134
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,720
Lina,

135
00:10:40,490 --> 00:10:42,290
I brought over the fish your dad caught

136
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,080
and also a lot of groceries.

137
00:10:44,288 --> 00:10:45,490
You don't need to come down.

138
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:47,770
By the way,

139
00:10:48,650 --> 00:10:49,960
who let Le Shuishan move in?

140
00:10:50,244 --> 00:10:51,355
What's the situation now?

141
00:10:51,560 --> 00:10:54,250
Should I go upstairs and say hello?

142
00:10:54,410 --> 00:10:54,960
Oppo.

143
00:10:56,130 --> 00:10:56,530
Wait.

144
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,050
She's down here.

145
00:10:58,050 --> 00:11:00,130
- I miss you so much.
- Get up now.

146
00:11:00,680 --> 00:11:02,130
Are you being good?

147
00:11:02,170 --> 00:11:03,200
Why isn't Shen with her?

148
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:04,400
All right, I'm hanging up.

149
00:11:05,377 --> 00:11:06,800
He's been behaving at my place.

150
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:07,530
Really?

151
00:11:07,560 --> 00:11:08,720
But he won't eat.

152
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,960
You didn't eat?

153
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,200
Why not?

154
00:11:16,890 --> 00:11:17,890
Le.

155
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:20,650
You're Le, right?

156
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:21,720
Hello.

157
00:11:21,890 --> 00:11:22,920
You don't know me?

158
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,600
I'm Lina's mom.

159
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,840
Nice to meet you, Mrs. Liu.

160
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:27,890
Nice to meet you, too.

161
00:11:30,170 --> 00:11:30,890
This dog...

162
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,440
This dog is so adorable.

163
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,370
I'm sorry.

164
00:11:34,530 --> 00:11:35,410
He's shy.

165
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,290
Did he bite you?

166
00:11:36,770 --> 00:11:37,840
No worries.

167
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,490
He doesn't bite.

168
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:39,410
I know.

169
00:11:48,490 --> 00:11:48,920
Lina.

170
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:50,440
Lina.

171
00:11:51,170 --> 00:11:51,530
Lina.

172
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:52,050
Mom.

173
00:11:52,177 --> 00:11:54,266
Do you know who I ran into downstairs
just now?

174
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:54,840
Who?

175
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,290
Le Shuishan

176
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,920
and a big guy.

177
00:11:58,511 --> 00:11:59,890
They were feeding the dog together.

178
00:12:00,890 --> 00:12:03,370
The three of them
looked so peaceful together.

179
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:05,890
Big guy?

180
00:12:07,250 --> 00:12:08,920
That's her ex-boyfriend.

181
00:12:11,050 --> 00:12:11,680
My goodness.

182
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:13,320
Ex-boyfriend?

183
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,720
Her ex came here?

184
00:12:16,770 --> 00:12:18,130
Le Shuishan is really something.

185
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,960
She lives here
but hangs out with another guy.

186
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,200
She's nothing like Jingmin.

187
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,290
So ridiculous.

188
00:12:24,290 --> 00:12:25,177
Don't talk nonsense.

189
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:25,770
I...

190
00:12:27,890 --> 00:12:29,050
What's this?

191
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,680
What's this?

192
00:12:31,050 --> 00:12:32,320
Why is your mother-in-law's photo

193
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,010
here?

194
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:36,080
Mom.

195
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:36,888
What's going on?

196
00:12:37,370 --> 00:12:38,290
I brought it back.

197
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:41,600
You did?

198
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,770
Oh, well.

199
00:12:44,770 --> 00:12:47,080
Shen Qing, you're so kind.

200
00:12:47,111 --> 00:12:48,333
You married the right person.

201
00:12:50,022 --> 00:12:50,920
Mom, I'm off to work.

202
00:12:52,130 --> 00:12:53,560
Sure. Take care.

203
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:58,840
Well, go ahead. I'll take care of it.

204
00:12:59,010 --> 00:13:00,050
Sure. Thanks, Mom.

205
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:00,890
Yeah.

206
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:03,200
Be careful.

207
00:13:10,410 --> 00:13:13,290
Why care about Le Shuishan's feelings?

208
00:13:14,370 --> 00:13:15,890
To welcome a new woman,

209
00:13:16,410 --> 00:13:18,440
he moved

210
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,720
your mother-in-law's photo.

211
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,800
This is simply ridiculous.

212
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,010
He probably

213
00:13:25,010 --> 00:13:26,844
hasn't met someone like me in his life.

214
00:13:26,866 --> 00:13:28,440
I'm just worried he'll get back at you.

215
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,200
Him?

216
00:13:29,977 --> 00:13:30,955
Does he have the guts?

217
00:13:46,650 --> 00:13:47,410
Look!

218
00:13:47,466 --> 00:13:48,290
There's the big guy.

219
00:13:48,290 --> 00:13:49,600
Look. There he is.

220
00:13:50,155 --> 00:13:51,360
Le Shuishan's over there too.

221
00:13:53,170 --> 00:13:53,600
Shen Qing.

222
00:13:54,170 --> 00:13:54,600
Shen Qing.

223
00:13:54,890 --> 00:13:55,410
Go.

224
00:13:57,200 --> 00:13:57,680
Shen Qing.

225
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:58,170
Mom,

226
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:00,320
can you please stop?

227
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:02,000
Stop causing trouble for us again.

228
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,170
Are you Director Wu?

229
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:17,920
Yes, I am. You must be Professor Shen.

230
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:18,440
Yes.

231
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,720
Nice to meet you.

232
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,170
Zhang told me about this place.

233
00:14:21,650 --> 00:14:22,410
He mentioned you.

234
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,200
Oh, yes.

235
00:14:24,111 --> 00:14:25,800
Feel free to ask me
if you need anything.

236
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:26,440
Sure.

237
00:14:26,844 --> 00:14:28,000
I'd like to look into

238
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:31,680
the regulations
about job transfer in expedition

239
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:36,770
in 1988 and local policies

240
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:40,010
related to high-risk occupations.

241
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:43,410
1988?

242
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:45,080
That's over 30 years ago.

243
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:45,650
Yes.

244
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,320
Professor Shen,

245
00:14:50,010 --> 00:14:51,010
I can only try my best.

246
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:51,920
Sure.

247
00:14:51,955 --> 00:14:52,560
Thank you.

248
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:53,920
No trouble at all.

249
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,800
Sure.

250
00:15:23,444 --> 00:15:24,720
Sorry, I need to take this call.

251
00:15:32,290 --> 00:15:32,650
Hello?

252
00:15:33,370 --> 00:15:33,920
Shen,

253
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:36,290
I saw Tang Jialin.

254
00:15:37,320 --> 00:15:38,120
You found him?

255
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:41,050
He's at the main gate
of the chemical plant.

256
00:15:41,955 --> 00:15:42,770
He went inside.

257
00:15:44,311 --> 00:15:45,533
I've sent you the location.

258
00:15:49,250 --> 00:15:50,050
I'll hurry up.

259
00:15:54,690 --> 00:15:55,210
Ice,

260
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:58,770
I don't think what you did
was appropriate.

261
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:02,010
Since Mr. Lu raises concerns

262
00:16:02,770 --> 00:16:04,600
about the investment in RF,

263
00:16:05,311 --> 00:16:06,880
that means there are risks involved,

264
00:16:07,244 --> 00:16:08,840
and we should start an investigation.

265
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:12,050
But you had finance transfer the funds
so quickly.

266
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:14,560
Don't you think it was rash?

267
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:19,690
Mr. Qiao,

268
00:16:20,490 --> 00:16:22,400
RF is at a critical stage now.

269
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:24,290
They desperately need this money.

270
00:16:24,777 --> 00:16:26,844
I believe that since we've
signed the contract,

271
00:16:26,866 --> 00:16:28,333
we should show commitment.

272
00:16:28,888 --> 00:16:30,120
In venture capital investment,

273
00:16:30,730 --> 00:16:32,770
venture comes before investment.

274
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,450
We can't back out

275
00:16:34,955 --> 00:16:37,222
just because things don't seem
to be in our favor.

276
00:16:38,290 --> 00:16:39,400
What are you getting at?

277
00:16:41,290 --> 00:16:43,080
Didn't we put real money
into this before?

278
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,970
The venture is like the wind.

279
00:16:45,177 --> 00:16:46,640
Is it wrong to ride along the wind

280
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:48,640
and steer clear when there are risks?

281
00:16:48,866 --> 00:16:50,266
Where's your professional integrity?

282
00:16:51,530 --> 00:16:53,880
My professionalism includes
managing risks

283
00:16:54,450 --> 00:16:56,160
and pushing projects forward.

284
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:00,840
Mr. Qiao,

285
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:02,250
Mr. Lu,

286
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,490
if RF can't pass
the third clinical trial,

287
00:17:06,010 --> 00:17:07,930
the money we've invested
will go down the drain

288
00:17:07,977 --> 00:17:09,822
and cause a great loss to the company.

289
00:17:10,210 --> 00:17:11,290
As far as I'm concerned,

290
00:17:11,770 --> 00:17:13,800
RF has cut salaries
and minimized expenses.

291
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:15,400
The higher-ups

292
00:17:15,511 --> 00:17:16,930
even put in their personal savings

293
00:17:16,930 --> 00:17:18,400
just to push this project forward.

294
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:20,120
They've done all they can.

295
00:17:25,490 --> 00:17:27,840
You seem to know a lot about RF.

296
00:17:28,244 --> 00:17:30,400
So, how are
the third clinical trial's results?

297
00:17:30,555 --> 00:17:32,222
Can you guarantee anything?

298
00:17:33,250 --> 00:17:35,210
I know their R&D very well,

299
00:17:35,244 --> 00:17:36,800
and I'm very confident in them.

300
00:17:37,355 --> 00:17:38,490
You're confident in them?

301
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,640
If you think you stand a point,

302
00:17:40,733 --> 00:17:42,400
why didn't you explain this to everyone?

303
00:17:42,511 --> 00:17:44,770
Why did you make the transfer one minute
before closing?

304
00:17:45,360 --> 00:17:46,530
Were you afraid we'd stop you?

305
00:17:46,933 --> 00:17:49,133
I was acting according
to my professional judgment.

306
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:52,050
I did that with a clear conscience.

307
00:17:55,290 --> 00:17:56,160
Clear conscience?

308
00:17:58,210 --> 00:17:58,640
Ice,

309
00:17:59,770 --> 00:18:01,050
are you sure?

310
00:18:02,933 --> 00:18:04,120
What are you trying to say?

311
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,530
You and Mr. Shen from RF

312
00:18:07,800 --> 00:18:09,955
take the same night running route
every day.

313
00:18:10,266 --> 00:18:12,080
They eat stir-fried dumplings
in the morning

314
00:18:12,080 --> 00:18:12,840
and run at night.

315
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:15,160
You're so close.

316
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,930
Is there any secret deal between you?

317
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,600
It's natural for investors and founders

318
00:18:29,210 --> 00:18:31,400
to be interested in each other
and collaborate closely,

319
00:18:32,290 --> 00:18:34,600
but it doesn't involve
personal relationships.

320
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,010
I don't think

321
00:18:37,530 --> 00:18:39,770
eating stir-fried dumplings together
means anything more.

322
00:18:50,450 --> 00:18:51,360
If the company

323
00:18:52,050 --> 00:18:53,080
questions my decisions,

324
00:18:54,970 --> 00:18:56,490
it means our values aren't aligned.

325
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:02,530
I see no reason to stay.

326
00:19:04,320 --> 00:19:04,840
I'll resign.

327
00:19:06,666 --> 00:19:08,970
You resign
right after the funds were transferred.

328
00:19:09,530 --> 00:19:11,320
That makes me suspicious of you.

329
00:19:12,840 --> 00:19:13,450
You

330
00:19:14,288 --> 00:19:16,000
will be suspended for investigation.

331
00:19:21,155 --> 00:19:22,377
Do as you see fit.

332
00:19:33,970 --> 00:19:35,930
Dr. Qin, I just signed.

333
00:19:35,970 --> 00:19:37,555
The money will come through today.

334
00:19:38,490 --> 00:19:39,250
Don't worry.

335
00:19:39,730 --> 00:19:41,560
The B+ round funding came in.

336
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:43,800
Okay.

337
00:19:44,288 --> 00:19:45,800
Let me know if anything comes up.

338
00:19:45,970 --> 00:19:46,450
Sure.

339
00:19:54,355 --> 00:19:56,973
(An Ruifeng)

340
00:19:56,998 --> 00:20:00,370
(Ice has been suspended
for investigation.)

341
00:20:06,630 --> 00:20:10,020
(Ice Li)

342
00:20:11,530 --> 00:20:12,050
Hello.

343
00:20:12,530 --> 00:20:15,120
