347
00:20:23,466 --> 00:20:24,600
Please try again later.

348
00:20:29,891 --> 00:20:34,770
(Honest, Innovative,
Eco-friendly, Communal)

349
00:20:34,888 --> 00:20:36,400
How could you allow this to happen?

350
00:20:38,530 --> 00:20:39,840
Rules are rules.

351
00:20:40,444 --> 00:20:41,822
Tell them to put up with it.

352
00:20:44,290 --> 00:20:44,730
Jeez.

353
00:20:44,777 --> 00:20:46,711
You can't even handle something
this trivial.

354
00:20:57,080 --> 00:20:58,120
This place is nice.

355
00:21:00,690 --> 00:21:01,010
You...

356
00:21:09,450 --> 00:21:10,730
Are you here to pick a fight?

357
00:21:11,555 --> 00:21:12,880
There are cameras up there

358
00:21:14,466 --> 00:21:15,840
and security guards downstairs.

359
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:18,010
If you break the law,

360
00:21:19,490 --> 00:21:21,250
I'll report you immediately.

361
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:23,770
The canoe team will fire you,

362
00:21:23,770 --> 00:21:25,730
believe it or not?

363
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:32,360
Mr. Tang, why are you
being so aggressive?

364
00:21:32,770 --> 00:21:34,450
We didn't mean any harm.

365
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,120
We just came here

366
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,290
to catch up on old times

367
00:21:39,050 --> 00:21:40,120
peacefully.

368
00:21:43,222 --> 00:21:44,755
And you even came to my workplace.

369
00:21:45,450 --> 00:21:48,080
If you could find Le Shuishan's place,

370
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:51,290
why wouldn't we be able
to find your office?

371
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:55,160
You...

372
00:21:55,730 --> 00:21:56,050
Don't.

373
00:21:57,880 --> 00:21:59,120
This is a small world.

374
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:00,770
We will cross paths eventually.

375
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:03,290
Unless you can fly away.

376
00:22:05,050 --> 00:22:07,560
What exactly do you want?

377
00:22:09,840 --> 00:22:10,880
Didn't I tell you just now?

378
00:22:11,490 --> 00:22:13,050
We're here to catch up on old times.

379
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:18,930
We want you to apologize to Le Shuishan

380
00:22:19,560 --> 00:22:21,970
and her late husband, Zhang Yali.

381
00:22:24,010 --> 00:22:24,930
That's impossible.

382
00:22:27,450 --> 00:22:28,730
You've hurt your leg.

383
00:22:29,560 --> 00:22:30,840
Did you hurt your brain too?

384
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:33,320
Do you have no shame?

385
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:35,080
Watch your words.

386
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:38,640
Have a look at this document.

387
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:40,600
Listen up.

388
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:44,770
This is the headquarters personnel
transfer expedition regulation.

389
00:22:44,770 --> 00:22:46,210
Regulations No. 36.

390
00:22:50,730 --> 00:22:52,160
This is Article 4:

391
00:22:52,530 --> 00:22:54,840
Anyone involved in high-risk work

392
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:57,010
such as extraction, drilling,
or expedition

393
00:22:57,066 --> 00:22:58,844
must undergo
a medical history assessment.

394
00:22:59,120 --> 00:23:00,320
Anyone with heart disease,

395
00:23:00,530 --> 00:23:03,160
lung disease, high blood pressure,
diabetes, or other conditions

396
00:23:03,266 --> 00:23:05,120
is not allowed to participate
in extraction,

397
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:06,690
drilling, or expedition.

398
00:23:08,840 --> 00:23:09,400
See this?

399
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:12,290
This is Zhang Yali's medical record.

400
00:23:14,290 --> 00:23:16,690
It's written here,
rheumatic heart disease.

401
00:23:17,840 --> 00:23:18,800
And atrial fibrillation.

402
00:23:20,840 --> 00:23:22,290
In that same month and the same year,

403
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,050
after you reviewed this medical record

404
00:23:24,050 --> 00:23:25,250
and this document,

405
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,320
you issued this order.

406
00:23:26,530 --> 00:23:29,600
It says here, "Overcome difficulties.
Depart immediately."

407
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:30,530
By Tang Jialin.

408
00:23:31,250 --> 00:23:31,730
Was it you?

409
00:23:32,050 --> 00:23:32,840
Take a good look.

410
00:23:35,050 --> 00:23:36,840
Where did you find this?

411
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:41,690
Someone righteous
stepped forward to help,

412
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:46,770
and someone combed through
every book.

413
00:23:47,530 --> 00:23:48,490
Do you think

414
00:23:48,930 --> 00:23:49,730
Le Shuishan

415
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,120
didn't sue you

416
00:23:51,770 --> 00:23:52,770
because she forgave you?

417
00:23:53,970 --> 00:23:55,360
Do you see her as a pushover?

418
00:23:56,210 --> 00:23:56,490
Well.

419
00:23:56,690 --> 00:23:59,010
What's the point of bringing this out?

420
00:24:00,210 --> 00:24:03,770
This only proves my negligence of duty.

421
00:24:04,530 --> 00:24:06,400
I overlooked his heart condition.

422
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:08,880
My vision was poor.

423
00:24:09,250 --> 00:24:11,450
I didn't read
his medical record carefully.

424
00:24:11,770 --> 00:24:14,120
Besides, the statute of limitations
has passed.

425
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:15,690
I'm not scared of a lawsuit.

426
00:24:19,490 --> 00:24:20,160
Shen,

427
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:22,450
I told you.

428
00:24:24,210 --> 00:24:25,400
Words don't work

429
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:28,640
on rascals like him.

430
00:24:29,320 --> 00:24:30,400
You have to use your fists.

431
00:24:30,560 --> 00:24:30,880
No.

432
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:31,320
Heibao,

433
00:24:32,044 --> 00:24:32,880
I agree with you.

434
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:35,120
But let me say one thing
before you do.

435
00:24:36,133 --> 00:24:37,770
The status of limitations has expired,

436
00:24:37,955 --> 00:24:40,266
and the court
can't hold you accountable.

437
00:24:40,690 --> 00:24:41,250
However,

438
00:24:42,250 --> 00:24:45,210
what you did can't be erased.

439
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:47,360
We might not sue you,

440
00:24:47,690 --> 00:24:49,690
but we can

441
00:24:50,490 --> 00:24:52,050
let everyone know

442
00:24:52,560 --> 00:24:54,080
what kind of person you are.

443
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:56,400
We'll expose all the filthy things
you've done.

444
00:24:56,422 --> 00:24:58,155
Let's see if you can
still sit comfortably.

445
00:24:58,560 --> 00:24:59,010
Right.

446
00:25:00,050 --> 00:25:01,930
We agreed

447
00:25:01,930 --> 00:25:03,600
not to threaten me.

448
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:05,210
We're not threatening you.

449
00:25:05,770 --> 00:25:08,290
We're serious about this.

450
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:14,640
Look at this photo.

451
00:25:15,450 --> 00:25:16,080
Look.

452
00:25:17,080 --> 00:25:18,160
Look at Zhang Yali.

453
00:25:19,450 --> 00:25:20,530
Now, look at yourself.

454
00:25:21,210 --> 00:25:23,050
You think you didn't owe him anything?

455
00:25:23,244 --> 00:25:25,688
Can you really face your children
and grandchildren?

456
00:25:27,844 --> 00:25:29,840
If you don't apologize today,
this won't be over.

457
00:25:30,120 --> 00:25:30,450
Wait...

458
00:25:30,930 --> 00:25:32,360
Shen, don't waste your breath on him.

459
00:25:33,450 --> 00:25:35,730
We'll go to the disciplinary board

460
00:25:36,800 --> 00:25:38,250
to expose him.

461
00:25:38,377 --> 00:25:38,840
Let's go.

462
00:25:39,290 --> 00:25:40,290
Hold on.

463
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:40,970
Hold on.

464
00:25:42,640 --> 00:25:44,290
Don't be mad.

465
00:25:47,690 --> 00:25:48,210
I...

466
00:25:50,022 --> 00:25:50,770
I'll apologize.

467
00:25:52,840 --> 00:25:54,050
I'm willing to apologize.

468
00:25:58,755 --> 00:26:01,330
(I apologize to Le Shuishan
and Zhang Yali. By Tang Jialin)

469
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:02,490
He apologized.

470
00:26:04,050 --> 00:26:05,800
I don't need to fear him anymore.

471
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,490
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

472
00:26:12,210 --> 00:26:13,250
Not just me,

473
00:26:15,730 --> 00:26:16,840
Li Heibao helped you too.

474
00:26:18,050 --> 00:26:19,290
We've all got your back.

475
00:26:19,730 --> 00:26:21,320
He had to write a report

476
00:26:21,530 --> 00:26:23,320
for punching that Smiling Tiger.

477
00:26:24,690 --> 00:26:25,290
People say,

478
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:27,120
"With deep love protected,

479
00:26:27,560 --> 00:26:28,930
it's like wearing armor

480
00:26:29,360 --> 00:26:30,730
and holding a sword."

481
00:26:33,250 --> 00:26:34,400
If you want to sue him,

482
00:26:35,010 --> 00:26:35,360
this is

483
00:26:36,530 --> 00:26:37,600
your evidence.

484
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:41,250
If you want to let it go,

485
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,320
this is still your weapon.

486
00:26:45,320 --> 00:26:45,880
Either way,

487
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,360
with the evidence,

488
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,800
he won't dare bother you again.

489
00:27:01,911 --> 00:27:02,770
Even if I sue him,

490
00:27:05,050 --> 00:27:07,250
Yali and my kid won't come back.

491
00:27:13,210 --> 00:27:14,970
Mr. Shen, I just want to live peacefully

492
00:27:15,160 --> 00:27:17,490
for the rest of my life

493
00:27:18,010 --> 00:27:18,840
without

494
00:27:20,250 --> 00:27:21,970
shadows casting over me.

495
00:27:23,690 --> 00:27:25,250
At least I have this now.

496
00:27:26,970 --> 00:27:28,530
This is justice for me.

497
00:27:30,730 --> 00:27:31,290
Thank you.

498
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:33,120
Thank you.

499
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:35,880
Thank you.

500
00:27:38,800 --> 00:27:39,250
Thank you.

501
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,280
(Have you heard about that?)

502
00:27:55,288 --> 00:27:56,360
(Ice has been suspended.)

503
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:57,800
(It's because of RF.)

504
00:27:58,120 --> 00:27:59,690
(They say she was close with Mr. Shen.)

505
00:28:08,371 --> 00:28:14,800
(Ice Li)

506
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:58,160
Cheers.

507
00:28:58,450 --> 00:29:01,450
Let's celebrate Duole's video
hitting over 100,000 views.

508
00:29:02,010 --> 00:29:04,690
I wish my son a bright future
and great success.

509
00:29:08,311 --> 00:29:08,930
Let's dig in.

510
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:09,800
Here.

511
00:29:10,050 --> 00:29:11,120
Dad, try this steak.

512
00:29:12,111 --> 00:29:12,822
Here you go.

513
00:29:12,822 --> 00:29:13,600
Thank you, Duole.

514
00:29:14,360 --> 00:29:15,320
Mom, have some too.

515
00:29:15,730 --> 00:29:16,640
You're the goddess.

516
00:29:17,600 --> 00:29:18,840
You've really grown up.

517
00:29:18,888 --> 00:29:19,600
So thoughtful.

518
00:29:19,730 --> 00:29:20,120
Come.

519
00:29:20,120 --> 00:29:20,933
He can do it himself.

520
00:29:20,977 --> 00:29:21,555
You eat too.

521
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:22,010
Eat up.

522
00:29:24,360 --> 00:29:25,530
Why aren't you filming today?

523
00:29:27,666 --> 00:29:28,530
Oh, that reminds me.

524
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:33,160
I'm enjoying this great meal
my son treated me to.

525
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:34,450
Dad,

526
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:36,870
I want to apply to
the Department of Directing.

527
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:37,711
What do you think?

528
00:29:37,711 --> 00:29:38,422
You're at it again.

529
00:29:38,422 --> 00:29:40,050
Directing? Why do you
want to study that?

530
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:40,490
Mom,

531
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:42,930
my video hit 100,000 views.

532
00:29:42,930 --> 00:29:44,320
I'm a genius.

533
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,980
It'd be too bad if I didn't study that.

534
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:46,880
Stop bragging.

535
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:49,930
Duole, I think that's a good idea.

536
00:29:50,111 --> 00:29:52,360
If you study what you like,
it'll be much easier for you.

537
00:29:53,360 --> 00:29:53,970
See?

538
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:55,560
My dad knows me well.

539
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:58,210
Yes, he knows you well.

540
00:29:58,444 --> 00:29:59,977
But does he actually do anything?

541
00:30:00,133 --> 00:30:02,590
All he does is support you
but never take real responsibility.

542
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:04,733
I'm the one who takes care of everything
in the end.

543
00:30:04,930 --> 00:30:06,120
What do you mean by that?

544
00:30:07,770 --> 00:30:09,600
Do you know how expensive art school is?

545
00:30:09,970 --> 00:30:11,880
It costs way more than regular majors.

546
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,010
We're not a well-off family.

547
00:30:14,010 --> 00:30:15,066
Arts just aren't for us.

548
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:17,080
Kids from ordinary families

549
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:19,466
should study finance or
pick up a skill, isn't that better?

550
00:30:20,600 --> 00:30:21,970
But I like it, Mom.

551
00:30:22,290 --> 00:30:23,770
Hobbies can't put food on the table.

552
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:26,640
Can you not kill his passion?

553
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:29,490
You should encourage him
to do something he loves.

554
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,080
Duole,

555
00:30:32,050 --> 00:30:33,360
I studied accounting.

556
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,970
I didn't like it,

557
00:30:35,210 --> 00:30:37,490
so I changed my career in my thirties.

558
00:30:38,290 --> 00:30:39,290
If you hadn't done that,

559
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:40,933
Duole could've studied what he loved.

560
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:43,770
You put all the money
into the investment.

561
00:30:43,770 --> 00:30:45,050
How are you going to support him?

562
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:45,800
Mom.

563
00:30:47,250 --> 00:30:47,690
Liu Lina,

564
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:49,930
Duole invited us to celebrate,

565
00:30:49,970 --> 00:30:50,880
not to argue.

566
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:52,930
I don't want to argue either.

567
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:55,880
I just want to let him know
that he should stay grounded.

568
00:30:56,600 --> 00:30:59,010
If you don't have the ability,
don't pursue your dream.

569
00:30:59,050 --> 00:30:59,970
You won't reach them.

570
00:31:00,050 --> 00:31:01,360
Who are you hinting at?

571
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:09,730
Duole,

572
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:10,560
I'm sorry.

573
00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:12,640
Dad.

574
00:31:13,422 --> 00:31:14,311
Come back.

575
00:31:14,488 --> 00:31:16,511
Even if it's your treat,
don't waste the food.

576
00:31:16,511 --> 00:31:17,488
Finish the steak.

577
00:31:32,690 --> 00:31:34,160
When my mom had me,

578
00:31:34,690 --> 00:31:35,600
she had major bleeding.

579
00:31:36,222 --> 00:31:38,355
She had her uterus removed after that.

580
00:31:39,288 --> 00:31:40,511
I'm the only child

581
00:31:41,050 --> 00:31:42,120
in the family.

582
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:45,120
When I was a kid,

583
00:31:46,111 --> 00:31:47,911
my parents were always stationed abroad.

584
00:31:47,933 --> 00:31:49,160
I hardly saw them.

585
00:31:50,250 --> 00:31:50,600
Here.

586
00:31:58,806 --> 00:32:03,520
(I apologize to Le Shuishan
and Zhang Yali. By Tang Jialin)

587
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:06,360
The past is in the past.

588
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,490
I'll live my life well.

589
00:32:11,010 --> 00:32:11,880
Don't worry about me.

590
00:32:17,466 --> 00:32:19,400
Don't worry about her, mister and madam.

591
00:32:26,530 --> 00:32:27,560
I don't have kids,

592
00:32:27,666 --> 00:32:29,355
and my parents passed away early.

593
00:32:30,290 --> 00:32:31,050
A few years ago,

594
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:33,800
my mom passed.

595
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:37,210
My dad followed a year later.

596
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,280
Before this,

597
00:32:39,711 --> 00:32:41,240
they were buried in the village.

598
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:44,240
This willow tree

599
00:32:44,810 --> 00:32:46,530
looks just like the one

600
00:32:46,930 --> 00:32:48,680
we had in our hometown.

601
00:32:51,490 --> 00:32:51,930
Ms. Le,

602
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:53,930
since you haven't arrived at 2 PM,

603
00:32:53,977 --> 00:32:56,022
I figured you'd probably
come to visit your parents,

604
00:32:56,022 --> 00:32:57,088
so I came out to meet you.

605
00:32:57,111 --> 00:32:59,330
We were talking about
this big willow tree.

606
00:33:00,111 --> 00:33:02,410
This tree was actually transplanted
from Xishan Island.

607
00:33:02,755 --> 00:33:04,511
It stands guard over those
who rest here.

608
00:33:04,533 --> 00:33:05,333
It's full of life.

609
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:07,330
Ms. Le, you have fine taste

610
00:33:07,422 --> 00:33:08,920
in picking this plot for your parents.

611
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:11,066
The third plot in the third row
of Garden Ding

612
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:12,222
is an excellent location.

613
00:33:12,410 --> 00:33:13,720
High ground, wide view,

614
00:33:13,822 --> 00:33:14,810
surrounded by water,

615
00:33:14,970 --> 00:33:15,810
and near a creek.

616
00:33:15,866 --> 00:33:17,300
Plus, it's right next to your parents.

617
00:33:17,330 --> 00:33:18,222
It's in high demand.

618
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:19,466
Many people are interested.

619
00:33:19,488 --> 00:33:20,640
If you've decided,

620
00:33:20,733 --> 00:33:22,155
you can leave a deposit first.

621
00:33:25,120 --> 00:33:25,640
Sorry,

622
00:33:26,355 --> 00:33:27,511
I need to take this call.

623
00:33:27,711 --> 00:33:28,800
Don't let us keep you.

624
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:35,530
I really want to buy this spot.

625
00:33:38,370 --> 00:33:39,680
That way, when I pass away,

626
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:42,490
I can rest

627
00:33:43,370 --> 00:33:44,370
next to my parents.

628
00:33:45,666 --> 00:33:46,533
That sounds good.

629
00:33:47,466 --> 00:33:48,600
You can keep them company.

630
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:50,890
Mr. Shen.

631
00:33:53,410 --> 00:33:54,050
If

632
00:33:56,050 --> 00:33:58,120
we really get together,

633
00:33:59,410 --> 00:34:02,280
will you be buried with me

634
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:04,200
here?

635
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:23,560
Shen.

636
00:34:25,080 --> 00:34:26,410
Two women

637
00:34:27,330 --> 00:34:29,640
fighting over you, in life and death.

638
00:34:31,970 --> 00:34:33,890
What a lucky problem.

639
00:34:34,930 --> 00:34:35,530
Well,

640
00:34:36,160 --> 00:34:37,240
that's basically

641
00:34:38,450 --> 00:34:39,450
a proposal, isn't it?

642
00:34:40,160 --> 00:34:40,970
A burial proposal

643
00:34:41,666 --> 00:34:43,450
is more intense than
a marriage proposal.

644
00:34:47,890 --> 00:34:48,530
How about this?

645
00:34:49,720 --> 00:34:50,280
Split

646
00:34:50,680 --> 00:34:51,080
your ashes

647
00:34:51,640 --> 00:34:52,280
in two

648
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:54,066
so that you can keep two sides happy.

649
00:34:54,111 --> 00:34:54,850
No one gets upset.

650
00:34:55,930 --> 00:34:56,890
Use a scale

651
00:34:57,377 --> 00:34:58,370
to divide it equally.

652
00:34:59,410 --> 00:34:59,930
Well...

653
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:01,370
Are you two doing a cross-talk

654
00:35:02,266 --> 00:35:03,280
and using me as a joke?

655
00:35:03,733 --> 00:35:04,330
If so, I'll go.

656
00:35:04,930 --> 00:35:05,490
No.

657
00:35:05,777 --> 00:35:07,330
I'm helping you come up with ideas.

658
00:35:10,930 --> 00:35:12,240
Everyone should live each day

659
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:13,890
with joy.

660
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:20,050
You can promise her first.

661
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:21,530
As for what you'll do,

662
00:35:21,888 --> 00:35:22,850
you can decide later.

663
00:35:24,680 --> 00:35:25,720
You want me to say yes,

664
00:35:26,640 --> 00:35:27,760
but I don't really mean it?

665
00:35:28,890 --> 00:35:30,600
Isn't that disrespectful?

666
00:35:31,720 --> 00:35:32,930
If you don't want to say yes,

667
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:34,370
you'll be in trouble.

668
00:35:34,680 --> 00:35:35,850
You'll have to go home

669
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:37,490
and discuss it

670
00:35:37,930 --> 00:35:39,240
with Shen Qing and Shen Dai.

671
00:35:43,330 --> 00:35:44,010
Patience.

672
00:35:45,080 --> 00:35:45,450
Patience.

673
00:35:46,010 --> 00:35:46,600
Take your time

674
00:35:46,666 --> 00:35:47,370
to figure it out.

675
00:35:47,850 --> 00:35:48,240
No rush.

676
00:35:56,010 --> 00:35:57,200
Will you be buried together?

677
00:36:02,370 --> 00:36:05,120
How could she ask something
so outrageous?

678
00:36:05,930 --> 00:36:08,410
I was so kind to give her my room.

679
00:36:08,890 --> 00:36:09,640
Because of her,

680
00:36:09,890 --> 00:36:11,640
Mom's photo was moved to Qing's place.

681
00:36:11,733 --> 00:36:12,711
I can't agree with this!

682
00:36:12,810 --> 00:36:13,930
I'm calling her now.

683
00:36:13,930 --> 00:36:15,911
I was the one
who brought Mom's photo back.

684
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:16,850
Calm down.

685
00:36:17,410 --> 00:36:18,240
I can't calm down.

686
00:36:18,530 --> 00:36:20,240
She wants to be buried next to you, Dad.

687
00:36:20,410 --> 00:36:21,330
What about Mom?

688
00:36:21,490 --> 00:36:22,530
I can't accept it.

689
00:36:23,080 --> 00:36:23,410
Dad,

690
00:36:24,466 --> 00:36:25,955
this is really not appropriate.

691
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:28,490
Mom was your wife.

692
00:36:29,080 --> 00:36:30,490
You bought a companion grave.

693
00:36:31,490 --> 00:36:33,370
Both of you are the roots
of the Shen family.

694
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:34,530
You can't be separated.

695
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:36,680
Exactly.

696
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,860
If that happens, we'll have
to visit two graves in the future.

697
00:36:40,088 --> 00:36:40,640
Wait a second.

698
00:36:40,890 --> 00:36:42,600
Does that mean

699
00:36:42,890 --> 00:36:44,970
our names will be
on someone else's tombstone?

700
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:53,530
Grandpa,

701
00:36:54,711 --> 00:36:55,680
don't worry about it.

702
00:36:57,080 --> 00:36:58,330
The living matter most.

703
00:36:59,330 --> 00:37:00,280
Shen Duole,

704
00:37:00,577 --> 00:37:01,760
Grandma loved you so much.

705
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:04,010
You're betraying her, you know?

706
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:05,240
Shen Duole,

707
00:37:05,888 --> 00:37:06,890
don't give bad advice.

708
00:37:08,330 --> 00:37:09,200
When I die,

709
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:11,800
will you be okay with your dad
being buried with your stepmom?

710
00:37:12,490 --> 00:37:12,930
Mom,

711
00:37:14,050 --> 00:37:15,560
stop making this more complicated.

712
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:22,200
Grandpa,

713
00:37:23,810 --> 00:37:24,890
I'll ask Grandma tonight.

714
00:37:25,066 --> 00:37:27,666
She always comes to my dreams
whenever something big happens.

715
00:37:29,311 --> 00:37:30,755
Why is my mom so good to you?

716
00:37:32,050 --> 00:37:32,530
Grandpa,

717
00:37:33,600 --> 00:37:34,930
there's only one message from her

718
00:37:34,930 --> 00:37:35,890
every time she comes.

719
00:37:36,488 --> 00:37:37,760
She just wants you to be happy.

720
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,930
She'd support anything you do.

721
00:37:41,600 --> 00:37:43,530
What matters the most is being alive.

722
00:37:49,280 --> 00:37:50,450
That's true love, okay?

723
00:37:53,355 --> 00:37:55,050
Can you try to understand each other?

724
00:37:55,244 --> 00:37:56,640
Can't you be a little more tolerant?

725
00:38:18,600 --> 00:38:19,760
Split the ashes

726
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:21,240
in half?

727
00:38:21,555 --> 00:38:22,377
My goodness.

728
00:38:22,890 --> 00:38:23,490
How is that

729
00:38:24,050 --> 00:38:24,680
any different

730
00:38:24,680 --> 00:38:25,530
from dismemberment?

731
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:28,330
Mom, think before you speak.

732
00:38:28,530 --> 00:38:30,530
He's my father-in-law.

733
00:38:31,530 --> 00:38:31,930
Why?

734
00:38:31,930 --> 00:38:33,810
We're just talking at home.

735
00:38:38,930 --> 00:38:39,240
Lina.

736
00:38:40,010 --> 00:38:40,850
Liu Dong said

737
00:38:41,530 --> 00:38:43,120
each family pays an 8,000 yuan deposit

738
00:38:43,640 --> 00:38:44,810
to reserve the plot.

739
00:38:46,330 --> 00:38:46,680
I see.

740
00:38:47,810 --> 00:38:48,450
Well...

741
00:38:49,890 --> 00:38:50,560
Lina,

742
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:53,850
can you smell the bean curd knot?
Have they gone bad?

743
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:56,280
Dad, don't worry.

744
00:38:56,680 --> 00:38:57,280
Got it.

745
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:58,530
I'll take care of it.

746
00:38:58,890 --> 00:38:59,200
Okay.

747
00:39:01,080 --> 00:39:01,560
Smell it.

748
00:39:02,490 --> 00:39:04,330
I'm not sure about this.

749
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:06,970
They've gone bad.

750
00:39:07,370 --> 00:39:08,450
That rancid smell.

751
00:39:08,822 --> 00:39:09,700
I'll throw them away.

752
00:39:09,850 --> 00:39:10,370
Lina.

753
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,370
Lina, give them to me.

754
00:39:11,600 --> 00:39:12,050
I'll do it.

755
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:14,160
You eat.

756
00:39:14,330 --> 00:39:14,680
Eat.

757
00:39:16,200 --> 00:39:17,280
Lina,

758
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:19,120
I noticed

759
00:39:19,810 --> 00:39:20,160
Liu Dong

760
00:39:20,160 --> 00:39:22,050
has liked your WeChat posts.

761
00:39:22,680 --> 00:39:23,530
Ignore him.

762
00:39:24,010 --> 00:39:25,450
If he asks for a deposit or anything,

763
00:39:25,450 --> 00:39:26,120
do not agree.

764
00:39:27,511 --> 00:39:28,450
I'll be honest with you.

765
00:39:29,022 --> 00:39:30,890
I've picked out a spot
for my columbarium.

766
00:39:31,422 --> 00:39:33,410
It's behind your mother-in-law's
memorial park.

767
00:39:33,577 --> 00:39:34,750
It's under planning right now.

768
00:39:34,970 --> 00:39:36,280
They say it'll be ready

769
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:37,680
in 15 years.

770
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,080
By then,

771
00:39:39,530 --> 00:39:41,330
I'll be just about the time

772
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,560
to move in.

773
00:39:43,200 --> 00:39:45,050
Oh, come on.

774
00:39:45,600 --> 00:39:46,330
Why?

775
00:39:47,370 --> 00:39:49,080
I'll be in my eighties.

776
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,680
That's long enough to live.

777
00:39:51,160 --> 00:39:53,050
Isn't that great? A blessed death.

778
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:54,600
Listen.

779
00:39:55,600 --> 00:39:57,080
Don't bury me

780
00:39:57,111 --> 00:39:58,410
in the Liu family's plot.

781
00:40:00,370 --> 00:40:01,160
I raised you

782
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,200
and I'm not asking much.

783
00:40:02,244 --> 00:40:03,890
I have only one task for you.

784
00:40:05,930 --> 00:40:06,330
Sure.

785
00:40:06,330 --> 00:40:07,400
Can you do this for me?

786
00:40:20,490 --> 00:40:21,280
Come.

787
00:40:23,080 --> 00:40:23,720
Have a look.

788
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:27,120
Today, I made this specialty
from the Northwest.

789
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:30,280
Tea.

790
00:40:31,240 --> 00:40:32,240
And this.

791
00:40:33,010 --> 00:40:34,640
You like mug bean cake.

792
00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:35,120
Right.

793
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:35,970
I looked up

794
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:37,970
