795
00:40:38,911 --> 00:40:39,955
What do you think of it?

796
00:40:41,930 --> 00:40:42,930
A heart.

797
00:40:44,850 --> 00:40:45,530
Loving hearts.

798
00:40:46,080 --> 00:40:46,640
Loving hearts.

799
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,720
Come on and try it.

800
00:40:53,010 --> 00:40:54,530
The texture really takes me back

801
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:56,050
to when I was a kid.

802
00:40:56,600 --> 00:40:57,080
I made it!

803
00:40:58,010 --> 00:40:59,120
Delicious.

804
00:41:04,810 --> 00:41:05,490
Mr. Shen,

805
00:41:07,810 --> 00:41:09,680
I asked you before

806
00:41:10,444 --> 00:41:11,810
if we could be buried together...

807
00:41:13,050 --> 00:41:14,850
Have you thought about it?

808
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:18,330
Shuishan,

809
00:41:20,240 --> 00:41:21,680
to be honest,

810
00:41:22,370 --> 00:41:23,810
I've thought about it seriously.

811
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:26,120
I discussed it

812
00:41:26,970 --> 00:41:27,760
with my children.

813
00:41:29,850 --> 00:41:31,280
I still think

814
00:41:32,533 --> 00:41:33,600
