815
00:41:39,777 --> 00:41:41,044
It's not appropriate?

816
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:44,680
It's fine.

817
00:41:45,444 --> 00:41:47,000
I didn't mean to put you on the spot.

818
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:49,410
I'm fine

819
00:41:50,930 --> 00:41:52,640
being buried alone.

820
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:56,200
I'm fine with that.

821
00:42:02,050 --> 00:42:03,010
Don't go just yet.

822
00:42:04,370 --> 00:42:05,810
Stay a little longer.

823
00:42:20,050 --> 00:42:20,680
I thought

824
00:42:22,200 --> 00:42:23,450
