827
00:42:31,450 --> 00:42:32,490
you're all the same.

828
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:36,410
Is that how you see it?

829
00:42:39,680 --> 00:42:40,930
Then give me a little more time.

830
00:42:42,600 --> 00:42:43,977
Let me think about it again.

